00:37:10.280 --> 00:37:11.040
Uncle Liu

00:37:11.280 --> 00:37:12.160
Master Liu.

00:37:12.920 --> 00:37:14.120
What did Cui Wenkui say?

00:37:14.320 --> 00:37:16.320
He said he'll listen to you this time.

00:37:18.800 --> 00:37:20.880
Master Liu, how many men have you brought?

00:37:21.200 --> 00:37:22.920
100 guns and 1,000 people.

00:37:24.440 --> 00:37:25.360
Okay.

00:37:25.960 --> 00:37:26.880
Brother Xi.

00:37:27.160 --> 00:37:28.800
Go get Qinglong Fortress, Black Tiger Mountain

00:37:29.000 --> 00:37:31.160
and Liu Ye.

00:37:32.320 --> 00:37:33.680
Let's follow the original plan.

00:37:33.920 --> 00:37:35.760
You know the location.

00:37:35.960 --> 00:37:36.560
Okay.

00:37:41.040 --> 00:37:42.520
Brother, what about me?

00:37:43.000 --> 00:37:44.600
Sixth Master, you split up 100 soldiers

00:37:44.840 --> 00:37:46.400
and ambush them at three passageways.

00:37:46.640 --> 00:37:49.240
Take the rest of your men to Qinglong Fortress

00:37:50.080 --> 00:37:51.040
to Qinglong Fortress.

00:37:51.280 --> 00:37:52.000
Yes.

00:37:52.200 --> 00:37:53.360
When you get to Qinglong Fortress,

00:37:53.680 --> 00:37:55.080
you must follow Madam.

00:37:55.520 --> 00:37:57.000
Don’t leave her.

00:37:58.560 --> 00:38:00.280
OK, I’ll go now.

00:38:00.480 --> 00:38:01.600
I’ll leave

00:38:02.120 --> 00:38:03.240
to you.

00:38:07.200 --> 00:38:08.600
Brother, don't worry.

00:38:09.200 --> 00:38:10.560
Unless I die,

00:38:21.960 --> 00:38:23.920
Then what can I do?

00:38:26.240 --> 00:38:27.560
You don't have to do anything now.

00:38:28.240 --> 00:38:29.280
Just recuperate.

00:38:34.360 --> 00:38:36.040
Hope everything goes well.

00:38:36.640 --> 00:38:38.840
The song of military song, the Dadao Ring.

00:38:39.080 --> 00:38:41.440
We swear to destroy Hu Nu and leave Yuguan.

00:38:41.720 --> 00:38:44.120
I will only destroy the battlefield and die for the country.

00:38:44.400 --> 00:38:47.000
There's no need to return it.

00:38:47.360 --> 00:38:48.160
Recite it again.

