The military song should sing the Dadao Ring.

00:38:50.920 --> 00:38:53.200
We swear to destroy Hu Nu and leave Yuguan.

00:38:53.440 --> 00:38:55.800
I will only destroy the battlefield and die for the country.

00:38:56.000 --> 00:38:58.640
There's no need to return it.

