Okay.

00:38:59.920 --> 00:39:01.440
I'll teach you another song tomorrow.

00:39:01.680 --> 00:39:03.480
You can recite it and eat.

00:39:09.440 --> 00:39:10.280
Go back.

00:39:10.480 --> 00:39:11.560
Thank you.

00:39:14.360 --> 00:39:15.480
Wait.

00:39:19.400 --> 00:39:21.440
You asked me if I was a Communist Party. That's right.

00:39:21.680 --> 00:39:22.440
Yes.

00:39:22.600 --> 00:39:23.360
Why?

00:39:23.640 --> 00:39:26.000
Because I'm looking for someone called Wu Zhen.

00:39:26.600 --> 00:39:27.560
Do you know him?

00:39:27.760 --> 00:39:28.720
No.

00:39:29.320 --> 00:39:30.400
That's all.

00:39:38.240 --> 00:39:39.120
Wu Zhen.

00:40:18.080 --> 00:40:19.840
Listen.

00:40:28.960 --> 00:40:30.080
I'll knock you out.

00:40:30.280 --> 00:40:31.720
Someone is still following me outside.

00:40:32.160 --> 00:40:34.240
It's obviously their trap, right?

00:40:34.400 --> 00:40:35.520
How would I know?

00:40:35.720 --> 00:40:37.280
I'm here to serve you.

00:40:37.440 --> 00:40:39.120
I didn't know I would be beaten

00:40:39.360 --> 00:40:40.840
and follow you.

00:40:41.920 --> 00:40:43.800
If I'm not mistaken,

00:40:44.160 --> 00:40:45.080
after I left,

00:40:45.240 --> 00:40:46.320
they came to you.

00:40:46.480 --> 00:40:48.440
and told you how to deal with me.

00:40:48.600 --> 00:40:49.080
Really?

00:40:49.440 --> 00:40:50.920
You know that?

00:40:51.400 --> 00:40:52.680
Sister, please let me go.

00:40:52.880 --> 00:40:54.120
I'm just a fugitive.

00:40:54.560 --> 00:40:56.520
How much do you earn a month here?

00:40:56.760 --> 00:40:59.120
One silver coin and a peck of millet.

00:41:00.080 --> 00:41:01.560
I'll give you two more silver dollars.

00:41:01.880 --> 00:41:04.320
But you have to listen to them

00:41:04.600 --> 00:41:05.840
and listen to me in secret.

00:41:06.560 --> 00:41:07.640
OK?

00:41:08.080 --> 00:41:08.840
Yes.

00:41:09.040 --> 00:41:09.720
Just let me go.

00:41:09.880 --> 00:41:10.880
I'll listen to you.

00:41:12.840 --> 00:41:13.440
Let me go.

00:41:13.600 --> 00:41:14.760
As long as you listen to me.

00:41:14.960 --> 00:41:15.880
I will.

00:41:16.080 --> 00:41:16.840
Let me go.

00:41:18.720 --> 00:41:19.640
Untie me.

00:41:23.240 --> 00:41:24.320
Brother Weiquan

00:41:24.360 --> 00:41:26.560
I'll wait for you at Bug Ridge.

00:41:33.440 --> 00:41:34.840
Boss, I'm back.

00:41:35.200 --> 00:41:36.400
He said to tie up the leader.

00:41:36.840 --> 00:41:38.600
The rest are at your disposal.

00:41:41.080 --> 00:41:42.240
Ninth Brother, wait.

00:41:42.480 --> 00:41:43.280
Fourth Brother.

00:41:46.880 --> 00:41:48.080
Fourth Brother.

00:41:48.240 --> 00:41:49.280
What are you doing? Fourth Brother.

00:41:49.640 --> 00:41:50.400
Fourth Brother.

00:41:51.600 --> 00:41:53.760
Brother, what do you think he is doing?

00:41:55.640 --> 00:41:56.760
Brother, later,

00:41:56.920 --> 00:41:58.280
I need to go to Wu Zhen's place first.

00:41:58.520 --> 00:41:59.360
Take it as a gift for me.

00:41:59.600 --> 00:42:00.680
No, no, brother.

00:42:00.840 --> 00:42:02.400
Don't be afraid. I can't do it.

00:42:02.600 --> 00:42:03.120
I can't.

00:42:03.320 --> 00:42:04.600
I just want to see

00:42:04.840 --> 00:42:06.080
if he dares to touch my men.

00:42:06.240 --> 00:42:07.080
Brother, I can't.

00:42:07.240 --> 00:42:08.320
Deyou. Deyou.

00:42:08.760 --> 00:42:09.440
Come here.

00:42:19.040 --> 00:42:20.560
Uncle Huo, Uncle Meng.

00:42:29.720 --> 00:42:31.160
Are you Wu Zhen?

00:42:33.240 --> 00:42:34.200
Let me see.

00:42:36.200 --> 00:42:37.880
He's pretty good-looking.

00:42:38.160 --> 00:42:39.960
Much better than that gold tooth.

00:42:40.240 --> 00:42:41.960
He deserves to die.

00:42:42.160 --> 00:42:43.880
Uncle Huo, are you here

00:42:44.160 --> 00:42:45.480
